Compile command:

	dtc -O dtb -I dts sht30.dts -o sht30.dtbo

Add to device tree:
	
	raspberrypi:
		
		sudo dtoverlay sht30.dtbo
	
	other:
		
		mkdir /sys/kernel/config/device-tree/overlays/my_overlay
		cat my_overlay.dtbo > /sys/kernel/config/device-tree/overlays/my_overlay/dtbo

View device tree:

	dtc -I fs -O dts /proc/device-tree -o /tmp/dt.dts

